title: Moynahan marries New York businessman
text:
Moynahan marries New York businessman Actress announces wedding via Instagram Author: By Lisa Respers France CNN Published On: Oct 18 2015 01:06:09 PM EDT Updated 1 h Jamie McCarthy/Getty Images (CNN) - 
Actress Bridget Moynahan surprised fans recently with the news that she is now a married woman. 
The "Blue Bloods" star, who has a son with football player Tom Brady, married New York businessman Andrew Frankel at a ceremony on Saturday in the Hamptons on Long Island, New York. Moynahan posted a wedding picture on her Instagram account with the caption "Oh, by the way, guess what I just did." 
People reports that Frankel is co-president of Stuart Frankel and Co., a Wall Street institutional brokerage firm, and that the pair met through friends. Moynahan has an 8-year-old son, Jack, with New England Patriots quarterback Brady. Quick Clicks
